    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='216:243'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0002', 'SBCK', '006-1a' );" name="006-1a" class="pb">[006-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='243:250'>毛詩卷第六</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='250:260'>唐蟋蟀詁訓傳第十</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='260:305'><span class='krp-note'>唐者周成王之母弟叔虞所封也其地帝堯夏禹所/都之墟漢曰太原郡在古兾州大行恒山之西太原</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='305:350'><span class='krp-note'>大岳之野其南有晉水叔虞之子爕父因改爲晋侯/至六丗孫僖侯名司徒習堯儉約遺化而不能以礼</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='350:375'><span class='krp-note'>節之今詩今其/風俗故云唐也</span>毛詩國風　鄭氏箋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='375:394'>蟋蟀刺晉僖公也儉不中禮故作是詩以閔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='394:413'>之欲其及時以禮自虞樂也此晉也而謂之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='413:432'>唐夲其風俗憂深思逺儉而用禮乃有尭之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='432:483'>遺風焉<span class='krp-note'>憂深思逺謂宛其死矣百歳之後之類也蟋音/悉蟀所律反說文蟀作<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR2186' title='KR2186' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR2186.png'/>僖許其反史記作釐</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='483:515'><span class='krp-note'>侯中丁仲反樂音洛下/皆同思息嗣反注同</span>蟋蟀在堂歳聿其莫今我</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='515:542'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0002', 'SBCK', '006-1b' );" name="006-1b" class="pb">[006-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='542:581'>不樂日月其除<span class='krp-note'>蟋蟀蛬也九月在堂聿遂除去也箋/云我我僖公也蛬在堂歳時之候是</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='581:630'><span class='krp-note'>時農功畢君可以自樂矣今不自樂日月且過去䟺復睱/爲之謂十二月當復命農計耦耕事聿允橘反莫音暮除</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='630:667'><span class='krp-note'>直慮反注同蛬俱勇反沈又九共/反趨織也一名蜻蛚復扶又反</span>無巳太康職思其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='667:713'>居<span class='krp-note'>巳甚康樂職主也箋云君雖當自樂亦無甚大樂欲/其用禮爲節也又當主思扵所居之事謂國中政令</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='713:750'><span class='krp-note'>大音㤗徐勑佐反下同/居義如字恊韻音據</span>好樂無荒良士瞿瞿<span class='krp-note'>荒大/也瞿</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='750:799'><span class='krp-note'>瞿然顧禮義也箋云荒廢亂也良善也君之好樂不當至/扵廢亂政事當如善士瞿瞿然顧禮義也好呼報反下同</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='799:823'><span class='krp-note'>瞿俱/具反</span>蟋蟀在堂歳聿其逝今我不樂日月其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='823:859'>邁<span class='krp-note'>邁行/也</span>無巳太康職思其外<span class='krp-note'>外禮樂之外箋云外/至四竟○礼樂之外</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='859:894'><span class='krp-note'>此一樂/字音岳</span>好樂無荒良士蹶蹶<span class='krp-note'>蹶蹶動而敏枚/事蹶俱衞反</span>蟋蟀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='894:926'>在堂役車其休<span class='krp-note'>箋云庻人乗役車役/車休農功畢無事也</span>今我不樂日</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='926:953'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0002', 'SBCK', '006-2a' );" name="006-2a" class="pb">[006-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='953:987'>月其慆<span class='krp-note'>慆過也慆/吐刀反</span>無巳太康職思其憂<span class='krp-note'>憂可憂也/箋云憂者</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='987:1020'><span class='krp-note'>謂鄰國侵/伐之憂</span>好樂無荒良士休休<span class='krp-note'>休休樂道之/心休許求反</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='1020:1033'>　　　　蟋蟀三章章八句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='1033:1052'>山有樞刺晉昭公也不能修道以正其國有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='1052:1071'>財不能用有鐘鼔不能以自樂有朝廷不能</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='1071:1090'>洒掃政荒民散將以危亡四鄰謀取其國家</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='1090:1120'>而不知國人作詩以刺之也<span class='krp-note'>樞夲或作蓲烏侯/反荎也昭公左傳</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='1120:1167'><span class='krp-note'>及史記作昭侯樂音洛下及注同朝直遥反廷徒佞反/洒所懈反沈所寄反下同掃蘇報反夲又作掃下同</span>山</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='1167:1209'>有樞隰有榆<span class='krp-note'>興也樞荎也國君有財貨而不能用如山/隰不能自用其財榆以朱反荎田節反沈</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='1209:1233'><span class='krp-note'>又直/梨反</span>子有衣裳弗曵弗婁子有車馬弗馳弗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='1233:1260'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0002', 'SBCK', '006-2b' );" name="006-2b" class="pb">[006-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='1260:1287'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0002', 'SBCK', '006-2b' );" name="006-2b" class="pb">[006-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='1287:1315'>彊昭公微弱國人將叛而歸沃焉<span class='krp-note'>封沃者封叔/父桓叔于沃</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='1315:1356'><span class='krp-note'>也沃曲沃晉之/邑也沃烏毒反</span>揚之水白石鑿鑿<span class='krp-note'>興也鑿鑿然鮮明/貌箋云激揚之水</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='1356:1405'><span class='krp-note'>波流湍疾洗去垢濁使白石鑿鑿然興者喻桓叔盛強除/民所惡民得以有礼義也鑿子洛反激經歴反湍吐端反</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1405:1441'><span class='krp-note'>洗蘇禮反又蘇典反去羗吕反/垢古口反惡烏路反又如字</span>素衣朱襮從子于沃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1441:1490'><span class='krp-note'>襮領也諸侯繡黼丹朱中衣沃曲沃箋云繡當爲綃綃黼/丹朱中衣中衣以綃黼爲領丹朱爲純囯人欲進此服去</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1490:1539'><span class='krp-note'>從桓叔襮音博字林方沃反繡音秀衆家申毛並依字下/文同鄭改爲宵黼音甫宵音消夲亦作綃純真允反又真</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1539:1572'><span class='krp-note'>順/反</span>旣見君子云何不樂<span class='krp-note'>箋云君子謂/桓叔樂音洛</span>揚之水白石</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1572:1607'>皓皓<span class='krp-note'>皓皓㓗白也/皓古老反</span>素衣朱繡從子于鵠<span class='krp-note'>繡黼也鵠/曲沃邑也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1607:1636'><span class='krp-note'>鵠户/毒反</span>旣見君子云何其憂<span class='krp-note'>言無/憂也</span>揚之水白石</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1636:1670'>粼粼<span class='krp-note'>粼粼清澈也粼利新反夲又/作磷同澈直列反或作徹誤</span>我聞有命不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1670:1697'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0002', 'SBCK', '006-3a' );" name="006-3a" class="pb">[006-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1697:1736'>敢以告人<span class='krp-note'>聞曲沃有善政命不敢以告人箋云不/敢以告人而去者畏昭公謂巳動民心</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1736:1755'>　　　揚之水三章二章章六句一章四句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1755:1774'>椒聊刺晉昭公也君子見沃之盛彊能脩其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1774:1801'>政知其蕃衍盛大子孫將有晉國焉<span class='krp-note'>椒木名聊/亂也蕃音</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1801:1838'><span class='krp-note'>煩衍延/善反</span>椒聊之實蕃衍盈升<span class='krp-note'>興也椒聊椒也箋云/椒之性芬香而少實</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1838:1887'><span class='krp-note'>今一捄之實蕃衍滿升非其常也興者喻桓叔晉君之支/别耳今其子孫衆多將日以盛也捄音求又其菊反何音</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1887:1926'><span class='krp-note'>掬沈居/局反</span>彼其之子碩大無朋<span class='krp-note'>朋比也箋云之子是子/也謂桓叔也碩謂壯貌</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1926:1975'><span class='krp-note'>佼好也大謂德美廣博也無朋平均不朋黨比王肅孫毓/申毛必履反謂無比例也一音必二反鄭云不朋黨則王</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1975:2017'><span class='krp-note'>申毛作毗至/反佼古夘反</span>椒聊且逺條且<span class='krp-note'>條長也箋云椒之氣目/益逺長似桓叔之德彌</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='2017:2054'><span class='krp-note'>廣博且子/餘反下同</span>椒聊之實蕃衍盈匊<span class='krp-note'>兩手曰匊匊夲/又作掬九六反</span>彼</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='2054:2081'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0002', 'SBCK', '006-3b' );" name="006-3b" class="pb">[006-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='2081:2111'>其之子碩大且篤<span class='krp-note'>篤厚/也</span>椒聊且逺條且<span class='krp-note'>言聲之/逺聞也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='2111:2124'>　　　　椒聊二章章六句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='2124:2147'>綢繆刺晉亂也國亂則昬姻不得其時焉<span class='krp-note'>不/得</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='2147:2186'><span class='krp-note'>其時謂不及仲春之月/綢直留反繆亡侯反</span>綢繆束薪三星在天<span class='krp-note'>興也綢/繆猶纒</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='2186:2235'><span class='krp-note'>綿也三星參也在天謂始見東方也男女待禮而成若薪/芻待人事而後束也三星在天可以嫁取矣箋云三星謂</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='2235:2284'><span class='krp-note'>心星也心有尊卑夫婦父子之象又爲二月之合宿故嫁/取者以爲候焉昬而火星不見嫁取之時也今我束薪扵</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='2284:2333'><span class='krp-note'>野乃見其在天則三月之末四月之中見於東方矣故云/不得其時參所金反見賢遍反下不見見於東同芻楚俱</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='2333:2372'><span class='krp-note'>反說文云芻刈草也象/苞束草之形宿音秀</span>今夕何夕見此良人<span class='krp-note'>良人美/室也箋</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='2372:2409'><span class='krp-note'>云今夕何夕者言此夕何月之/夕乎而女以見良人言非其時</span>子兮子兮如此良人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='2409:2453'>何<span class='krp-note'>子兮者嗟兹也箋云子兮子兮者斥嫁取者子/取後隂陽交㑹之月當如此良人何後户豆反</span>綢繆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='2453:2480'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0002', 'SBCK', '006-4a' );" name="006-4a" class="pb">[006-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='2480:2514'>束芻三星在隅<span class='krp-note'>隅東南隅也箋云心星在/隅謂四月之末五月之中</span>今夕何</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='2514:2556'>夕見此邂逅<span class='krp-note'>邂逅觧說之貌邂本亦作觧户懈反一音/户佳反逅亦作覯同胡豆反一音户溝反</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='2556:2590'><span class='krp-note'>邂覯觧說也韓詩云邂覯/不固之貌觧音蟹說音恱</span>子兮子兮如此邂逅何</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='2590:2627'>綢繆束楚三星在户<span class='krp-note'>參星正月中直户也箋云心星/在户謂五月之末六月之中直</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='2627:2665'><span class='krp-note'>音值又/如字</span>今夕何夕見此粲者<span class='krp-note'>三女爲粲大夫一妻二/妾粲采旦反字林作</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='2665:2676'>子兮子兮如此粲者何</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='2676:2689'>　　　　綢繆三章章六句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='2689:2708'>杕杜刺時也君不能親其宗族骨肉離散獨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='2708:2738'>居而無兄弟將爲沃所并爾<span class='krp-note'>杕徒細反本或作/夷狄字非也下篇</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='2738:2773'><span class='krp-note'>同并必/政反</span>有杕之杜其葉湑湑<span class='krp-note'>興也杕特生皃杜/赤棠也湑湑枝葉</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='2773:2800'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0002', 'SBCK', '006-4b' );" name="006-4b" class="pb">[006-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='2800:2829'><span class='krp-note'>不相比也湑私/叙反比毗志反</span>獨行踽踽豈無他人不如我同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='2829:2875'>父<span class='krp-note'>踽踽無所親也箋云他人謂異姓也言昭公逺其宗/族獨行於囯中踽踽然此豈無異姓之臣乎顧恩不</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='2875:2915'><span class='krp-note'>如同姓親親也踽/俱禹反遠于万反</span>嗟行之人胡不比焉<span class='krp-note'>箋云君所與/行之人謂異</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='2915:2953'><span class='krp-note'>姓卿大夫也比輔也此/人女何不輔君爲政令</span>人無兄弟胡不佽焉<span class='krp-note'>佽助/也箋</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='2953:2992'><span class='krp-note'>云異姓卿大夫女見君無兄弟之親/親者何不相推佽而助之佽七利反</span>有杕之杜其葉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='2992:3026'>菁菁<span class='krp-note'>菁菁葉盛也箋云菁菁希少/之貌菁夲又作青同子零反</span>獨行睘睘豈</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='3026:3062'>無他人不如我同姓<span class='krp-note'>睘睘無所依也同姓同祖也/睘本亦作㷀又作焭求營反</span>嗟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='3062:3079'>行之人胡不比焉人無兄弟胡不佽焉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='3079:3092'>　　　　杕杜二章章九句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='3092:3115'>羔裘刺時也晉人刺其在位不恤其民也<span class='krp-note'>恤/憂</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='3115:3142'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0002', 'SBCK', '006-5a' );" name="006-5a" class="pb">[006-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='3142:3179'><span class='krp-note'>也恤本亦作/䘏荀律反</span>羔裘豹祛自我人居居<span class='krp-note'>祛𬒮也夲末/不同在位與</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='3179:3228'><span class='krp-note'>民異心自用也居居懷惡不相親此之貌箋云羔裘豹袪/在位卿大夫之服也其役使我之民人其意居居然有悖</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='3228:3270'><span class='krp-note'>惡之心不恤我之困苦袪起居反又丘據/反居如字又音據比毗志反悖𥙷對反</span>豈無他人維</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='3270:3313'>子之故<span class='krp-note'>箋云此民卿大夫采邑之民也故云豈無他/人可歸往者乎我不去者乃念子故舊之人</span>羔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='3313:3348'>裘豹褎自我人究究<span class='krp-note'>褎猶祛也究究猶居居也褎/徐救反夲又作褏同宄九又</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='3348:3386'><span class='krp-note'>反爾雅云居/居究究惡也</span>豈無他人維子之好<span class='krp-note'>箋云我不去而/歸往他人者乃</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='3386:3414'><span class='krp-note'>念子而愛好之也民之厚如此/亦唐之遺風好呼報反注同</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='3414:3427'>　　　　羔裘二章章四句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='3427:3446'>鴇羽刺時也昭公之後大亂五丗君子下從</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='3446:3474'>征役不得養其父母而作是詩也<span class='krp-note'>大亂五世者/昭公孝侯鄂</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='3474:3501'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0002', 'SBCK', '006-5b' );" name="006-5b" class="pb">[006-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='3501:3528'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0002', 'SBCK', '006-5b' );" name="006-5b" class="pb">[006-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='3528:3545'>蓺稻梁父母何甞悠悠蒼天曷其有常</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='3545:3558'>　　　　鴇羽三章章七句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='3558:3577'>無衣美晉武公也武公始并晉國其大夫爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='3577:3605'>之請命乎天子之使而作是詩也<span class='krp-note'>天子之使是/時使来者并</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='3605:3645'><span class='krp-note'>卑政反下注同爲于/僞反使所使反注同</span>豈曰無衣七兮<span class='krp-note'>侯伯之礼七/命冕服七章</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='3645:3679'><span class='krp-note'>箋云我豈無是七章之衣/乎晉舊有之非新命之服</span>不如子之衣安且吉兮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='3679:3720'><span class='krp-note'>諸侯不命於天子則不成爲君箋云武公/𥘉并晉國心未自安故以得命服爲安</span>豈曰無衣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='3720:3767'>六兮<span class='krp-note'>天子之卿六命車旗衣服以六爲節箋云変七言六/者謙也不敢必當侯伯得受六命之服列於天子之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='3767:3807'><span class='krp-note'>卿猶愈乎不/愈羊主反</span>不如子之衣安且燠兮<span class='krp-note'>燠煖也燠本作奥/於六反煖奴緩反</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='3807:3820'>　　　　無衣二章章三句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='3820:3847'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0002', 'SBCK', '006-6a' );" name="006-6a" class="pb">[006-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='3847:3866'>有杕之杜刺晉武公也武公寡特兼其宗族</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='3866:3889'>而不求賢以自輔焉有杕之杜生于道左<span class='krp-note'>興/也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='3889:3938'><span class='krp-note'>道左之陽人所冝休息也箋云道左道東也日之熱恒在/日中之後道東之杜人所冝休息也今人不休息者以其</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='3938:3988'><span class='krp-note'>特生隂寡也興者喻武公𥘉兼其宗族不求賢者與之在/位君子不歸似乎特生之杜然○宗族本亦作宗矣隂於</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='3988:4026'><span class='krp-note'>鴆反又如字/夲亦作䕃同</span>彼君子兮噬肯適我<span class='krp-note'>噬逮也箋云肯/可適之也彼君</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='4026:4075'><span class='krp-note'>子之人至於此國皆可來之我君所君子之人義之與比/其不來者君不求之噬市丗反韓詩作逝逝及也比毗志</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='4075:4111'><span class='krp-note'>反</span>中心好之曷飲食之<span class='krp-note'>箋云曷何也言中心誠好/之何但飲食之當盡礼極</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='4111:4146'><span class='krp-note'>歡以待之好呼報反下同飲/扵鴆反下文同食音嗣下同</span>有杕之杜生于道周</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='4146:4180'><span class='krp-note'>周曲也○周/韓詩作右也</span>彼君子兮噬肯來遊<span class='krp-note'>遊觀也觀/古亂反</span>中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='4180:4189'>心好之曷飲食之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='4189:4216'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0002', 'SBCK', '006-6b' );" name="006-6b" class="pb">[006-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='4216:4231'>　　　　有杕之杜二章章六句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='4231:4254'>葛生刺晉獻公也好攻戰則國人多䘮矣<span class='krp-note'>䘮/棄</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='4254:4303'><span class='krp-note'>亡也夫從征役棄亡不反則其妻居家而怨思好呼報反/攻音貢又如字䘮息浪反注同又如字思息嗣反或如字</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='4303:4340'>葛生蒙楚蘞蔓于野<span class='krp-note'>興也葛生延而蒙楚蘝生蔓扵/野喻婦人外成於他家蘝音廉</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='4340:4382'><span class='krp-note'>又力恬反又力儉反徐又力劒反草木䟽云/似秳楼葉盛而細子正黒如燕薁不可食</span>予美亡此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='4382:4425'>誰與獨處<span class='krp-note'>箋云予我亡無也言我所美之人無於此謂/其君子也吾誰與居乎獨處家耳從軍未還</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='4425:4457'><span class='krp-note'>未知死生其/今無於此</span>葛生蒙棘蘝蔓于域<span class='krp-note'>域塋/域也</span>予美亡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='4457:4485'>此誰與獨息<span class='krp-note'>息止/也</span>角枕粲兮錦衾爛兮<span class='krp-note'>齊則/角枕</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='4485:4534'><span class='krp-note'>錦衾禮夫不在歛枕篋衾席韣而藏之箋云夫雖不在而/不失其祭也攝主主婦猶自齊而行事齊側皆反夲亦作</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='4534:4572'><span class='krp-note'>齋下同篋口牒反韣夲/亦作襡又作櫝徒木反</span>予美亡此誰與獨旦<span class='krp-note'>箋云/旦明</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='4572:4599'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0002', 'SBCK', '006-7a' );" name="006-7a" class="pb">[006-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='4599:4641'><span class='krp-note'>也我君子無於此吾/誰與齊乎獨自絜明</span>夏之日冬之夜<span class='krp-note'>言長也箋云思/者於晝夜之長</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='4641:4679'><span class='krp-note'>時尤甚故極/言之以盡情</span>百歳之後歸于其居<span class='krp-note'>箋云居墳墓也/言此者婦人專</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='4679:4708'><span class='krp-note'>壹義之至情之/盡墳符云反</span>冬之夜夏之日百歳之後歸于其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='4708:4727'>室<span class='krp-note'>室猶居也箋云室/猶塚壙壙音曠</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='4727:4740'>　　　　葛生五章章四句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='4740:4768'>采苓刺晉獻公也獻公好聽讒焉<span class='krp-note'>苓力丁反即/甘草葉似地</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='4768:4803'><span class='krp-note'>黄好呼/報反</span>采苓采苓首陽之巓<span class='krp-note'>興也苓大若也首/陽山名也采苓細</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='4803:4852'><span class='krp-note'>事也首陽幽辟也細事喻小行也幽辟喻無徴也箋云采/苓采苓者言采苓之人衆多非一也皆云采此苓於首陽</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='4852:4901'><span class='krp-note'>山之上首陽山之上信有苓矣然而今之采者未必於此/山然而人必信之興者喻事有似而非辟匹亦反下同行</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='4901:4938'><span class='krp-note'>下孟/反</span>人之爲言苟亦無信舎<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0999' title='KR0999' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0999.png'/>舎<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0999' title='KR0999' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0999.png'/>苟亦無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='4938:4965'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0002', 'SBCK', '006-7b' );" name="006-7b" class="pb">[006-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='4965:5018'>然<span class='krp-note'>苟誠也箋云苟且也爲言謂爲人爲善言以稱薦之/欲使見進用也<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0999' title='KR0999' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0999.png'/>之言焉也舎之焉舎之焉謂謗訕</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='5018:5067'><span class='krp-note'>人欲使見貶退也此二者且無信受之且無荅然爲于僞/反或如字下文皆同夲或作僞字非舎音捨下同旃之然</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='5067:5107'><span class='krp-note'>反訕所/諌反</span>人之爲言胡得焉<span class='krp-note'>箋云人以此言來不信受/之不荅然之從後察之或</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='5107:5137'><span class='krp-note'>時見罪/何所得</span>采苦采苦首陽之下<span class='krp-note'>苦苦/菜也</span>人之爲言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='5137:5175'>苟亦無與舎<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0999' title='KR0999' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0999.png'/>舎<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0999' title='KR0999' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0999.png'/>苟亦無然<span class='krp-note'>無與勿/用也</span>人之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='5175:5202'>爲言胡得焉采葑采葑首陽之東<span class='krp-note'>葑菜名也/葑孚容反</span>人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='5202:5235'>之爲言苟亦無從舎<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0999' title='KR0999' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0999.png'/>舎<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0999' title='KR0999' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0999.png'/>苟亦無然人之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='5235:5242'>爲言胡得焉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='5242:5255'>　　　　采苓三章章八句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='5255:5270'>唐國十二篇三十三章二百三句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='5270:5297'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0002', 'SBCK', '006-8a' );" name="006-8a" class="pb">[006-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='5297:5308'>秦車鄰詁訓傳第十一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='5308:5355'><span class='krp-note'>秦者隴西谷名也在雍州鳥䑕山之東北昔臯陶之子/伯翳佐禹治水有功舜命作虞賜姓曰嬴其末孫非子</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='5355:5402'><span class='krp-note'>爲周孝王飬馬於汧渭之間封爲附庸邑于秦谷及非/子之曽孫秦仲周宣王又命爲大夫仲之孫襄公討西</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='5402:5449'><span class='krp-note'>戎救周周室東遷以岐豊之地賜之始列爲諸侯春秋/時稱秦伯崔云秦在虞夏商爲諸侯至周爲附庸之國</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='5449:5469'>　　　　　　　　　　毛詩國風　鄭氏箋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='5469:5488'>車鄰美秦仲也秦仲始大有車馬禮樂侍御</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='5488:5524'>之好焉<span class='krp-note'>鄰本亦作隣又作轔栗人反/秦仲始大絶句或連下句非</span>有車鄰鄰有馬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='5524:5558'>白顚<span class='krp-note'>鄰鄰衆車聲也白顛的顙/也顛都田反的丁歷反</span>未見君子寺人之令</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='5558:5609'><span class='krp-note'>寺人内小臣也箋云欲見國君者必先令寺人使傳吿之時/秦仲又始有此臣寺如字又音侍本或作侍字寺人奄人内</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='5609:5653'><span class='krp-note'>小臣也令力呈反注同又力政反沈/力丁反韓詩作伶云使伶傳直專反</span>阪有漆隰有栗<span class='krp-note'>興/也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='5653:5680'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0002', 'SBCK', '006-8b' );" name="006-8b" class="pb">[006-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='5680:5723'><span class='krp-note'>陂者曰阪下濕曰隰箋云興者喻秦仲之君臣/所有各得其宜阪音反又扶板反陂彼寄反</span>旣見君</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='5723:5763'>子並坐鼓瑟<span class='krp-note'>又見其禮樂焉箋云旣見旣見秦仲也/並坐鼓瑟君臣以間暇燕飮相安樂也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='5763:5801'><span class='krp-note'>間音閑樂音/洛下文並同</span>今者不樂逝者其耋<span class='krp-note'>耋老也八十日/耋箋云今者不</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='5801:5852'><span class='krp-note'>於此君之朝自樂謂/仕焉而去仕他國其徒自使老言將/後寵禄也耋田節反一音天節反朝直遥反後胡豆反又如</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='5852:5878'><span class='krp-note'>字</span>阪有桑隰有楊旣見君子並坐鼓簧<span class='krp-note'>簧笙/也簧</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='5878:5900'><span class='krp-note'>音/黄</span>今者不樂逝者其亡<span class='krp-note'>亡喪/棄也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='5900:5918'>　　　車鄰三章一章四句二章章六句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='5918:5937'>駟鐵美襄公也始命有田狩之事園囿之樂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='5937:5980'>焉<span class='krp-note'>箋云始命命爲/諸侯也秦始附庸/也/駟鐵田結反又吐結反始命絶句囿音又</span>駟鐵孔阜六</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='5980:6017'>轡在手<span class='krp-note'>鐵驪阜大也箋云四馬六轡六轡/在手言馬之良也阜音符有反</span>公之媚子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='6017:6044'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0002', 'SBCK', '006-9a' );" name="006-9a" class="pb">[006-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='6044:6085'>從公于狩<span class='krp-note'>能以道媚于上下者冬獵曰狩箋云媚於/上下謂使君臣和合也此人從公往狩言</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='6085:6122'><span class='krp-note'>襄公親賢也/媚眉冀反</span>奉時辰牡辰牡孔碩<span class='krp-note'>時是辰時也冬/獻狼夏獻䴢春</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='6122:6168'><span class='krp-note'>秋獻鹿豕羣獸箋云奉是時牡者謂虞人也時牡/甚肥大言禽獸得其所也辰音純如字麋亡悲反</span>公曰左</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='6168:6214'>之舍拔則獲<span class='krp-note'>拔矢末也箋云左之者從禽之左射之也拔括/也舍拔則獲言公善射/舎音捨拔蒲末反射</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='6214:6254'><span class='krp-note'>食亦反括苦活反/善然去聲射音社</span>遊于北園四馬旣閑<span class='krp-note'>閑習也箋云/公所以田則</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='6254:6296'><span class='krp-note'>克獲者乃遊于北園之時時則巳習其四/種之馬北音不閑與閒同種章勇反上聲</span>輶車鸞鏕載</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='6296:6342'>獫歇驕<span class='krp-note'>輶輕也獫歇驕田犬也長喙曰獫短喙曰歇驕箋/云輕車驅逆之車也置鵉於鑣異於乗車也載始</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='6342:6393'><span class='krp-note'>也始田犬者謂達其搏噬始成之也此皆遊於北園時所爲/也輶由九反音由鵉羅端反鑣彼驕反獫力念反說文音力</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='6393:6444'><span class='krp-note'>見反歇本又作猲許謁反說文音火遏反驕本又作獢同許/喬反輕遣政反又如字下同驅丘遇反或丘于反乗仁正反</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='6444:6455'><span class='krp-note'>搏音博/舊音付</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='6455:6482'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0002', 'SBCK', '006-9b' );" name="006-9b" class="pb">[006-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='6482:6496'>　　　　　駟鐵三章章四句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='6496:6515'>小戎美襄公也備其兵甲以討西戎西戎方</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='6515:6534'>彊而征伐不休國人則矜其車甲婦人能閔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='6534:6577'>其君子焉<span class='krp-note'>箋云矜夸大也國人夸大其車甲之盛有樂/之意也婦人閔其君子恩義之至也作者叙</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='6577:6630'><span class='krp-note'>内外之志所以美君政教之功小戎兵車也鄭云羣臣/兵車/故曰小戎王云駕兩馬者矜居澄反夸苦花反樂音岳又音洛</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='6630:6669'>小戎俴収五楘梁輈<span class='krp-note'>俴淺収軫也五五束也楘歷録也/梁輈輈上勾衡也一輈五束束有</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='6669:6720'><span class='krp-note'>歷録箋云此羣臣之兵車故曰小戎輈陟留反/俴錢淺反収如字楘音木本又作鞪軫之忍反</span>游環脅驅<span class='krp-note'>叶/去</span>隂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='6720:6770'>靷鋈續<span class='krp-note'>游環靷環也游在/背上所以禦出也脅驅慎駕具所/以止入也隂揜軌也靷所以引也鋈白金也續續靷也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='6770:6825'><span class='krp-note'>箋云游環在背上無常處貫驂之外轡以禁其出脅驅者著服馬/之外脅以止驂之入揜軌在軾前垂輈上鋈續白金飾/續靷之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='6825:6878'><span class='krp-note'>環驅夲亦作駈起俱反靳居覲反靷之忍反鋈音沃舊音惡續/義如字徐辭屢反禦魚吕反慎或作順義亦兩通揜于撿反常</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='6878:6906'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0002', 'SBCK', '006-10a' );" name="006-10a" class="pb">[006-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='6906:6947'><span class='krp-note'>昌慮反服直畧反又丁畧反/軾音式本亦作式飾音失</span>文茵暢轂駕我騏馵<span class='krp-note'>文茵/虎皮</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='6947:7000'><span class='krp-note'>也暢轂長轂也騏騏文也左足白曰馵箋云此上六句者國人/所矜茵音因文茵以虎皮爲茵茵車席也暢勑亮反轂音/谷</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='7000:7039'><span class='krp-note'>騏音其馵/之樹反</span>言念君子温其如玉<span class='krp-note'>箋云言我也念君子/之性温然如玉玉有</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='7039:7079'><span class='krp-note'>五/德</span>在其板屋亂我心曲<span class='krp-note'>西戎板屋箋云心曲心之委/曲也憂則心亂也此上四句</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='7079:7106'><span class='krp-note'>者婦人所用/閔其君子</span>四牡孔阜六轡在手騏駵是中騧</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='7106:7152'>驪是驂<span class='krp-note'>黄馬黒喙曰騧箋云赤身黒鬛曰駵中中服也驂/兩騑也駵音留騧古花反鬛本又作/力輒反騑</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='7152:7191'><span class='krp-note'>芳非/反</span>龍盾之合鋈以觼軜<span class='krp-note'>龍盾畫龍其盾也合合而/載之軜驂内轡也箋云鋈</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='7191:7235'><span class='krp-note'>以觼軜軜之觼以白金爲飾也軜繫於軾前/盾順允反徐又音允觼古穴反軜音納内也</span>言念君子温</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='7235:7269'>其在邑<span class='krp-note'>在敵/邑也</span>方何爲期胡然我念之<span class='krp-note'>箋云方今以/何時爲還期</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='7269:7302'><span class='krp-note'>乎何以然了不/來言望之也</span>俴駟孔羣厹矛鋈錞蒙伐有苑<span class='krp-note'>俴/駟</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='7302:7330'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0002', 'SBCK', '006-10b' );" name="006-10b" class="pb">[006-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='7330:7381'><span class='krp-note'>四介馬也孔甚也厹三隅矛也錞鐏也蒙討羽也伐中干也/苑文貌箋云俴淺也謂以薄金爲介之札介甲也甚羣者言</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='7381:7432'><span class='krp-note'>和調也蒙厖也討雜也畫雜羽之文於伐故曰厖伐駟音肆/俴駟韓詩云駟馬不著甲曰俴駟厹音求三隅矛也錞徒對</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='7432:7490'><span class='krp-note'>反舊徒猥反一音敦說文云矛㦸下銅鐏蒙如字本或作<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR1691' title='KR1691' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1691.png'/>/音同鄭云厖也介音界鐏徂寸反又子遯反札側八反厖莫</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='7490:7522'><span class='krp-note'>江/反</span>虎韔鏤膺交韔二弓竹閉緄縢<span class='krp-note'>虎虎皮也韔/弓室也膺馬</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='7522:7571'><span class='krp-note'>帶也交韔交二弓於韔中也閉紲緄䋲縢約也箋云鏤膺/有刻金飾也韔勑亮反下同本亦作暢鏤魯豆反膺于澄</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='7571:7626'><span class='krp-note'>反閉悲位反本一作䩛鄭注周禮云弓檠曰/䩛弛則縳於弓裏/備損傷也以竹爲之䩛音悲位反徐邉患反一音必結反緄古本</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='7626:7653'><span class='krp-note'>反縢直登反/紲息列反</span>言念君子載寢載興厭厭良人秩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='7653:7699'>秩德音<span class='krp-note'>厭厭安靜也秩秩有知也箋云此旣閔其君子寢/起之勞又思其性與德也載音再載寢載興言思</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='7699:7750'><span class='krp-note'>之深而起居不寕也寢音青上聲興如字厭於賢反夊音燕/良音良秩陳乙反音直知去聲本亦作智音一陵切起如字</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='7750:7758'><span class='krp-note'>勞音/潦</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='7758:7786'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0002', 'SBCK', '006-11a' );" name="006-11a" class="pb">[006-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='7786:7799'>　　　　小戎三章章十句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='7799:7818'>蒹葭刺襄公也未能用周禮將無以固其國</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='7818:7865'>焉<span class='krp-note'>秦處周之舊土其人𬒳周之德敎日乆矣今襄公新/爲諸侯未習周之礼法故國人未服焉蒹古恬反葭</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='7865:7901'><span class='krp-note'>音加被/皮寄反</span>蒹葭蒼蒼白露爲霜<span class='krp-note'>興也蒹薕葭蘆也/蒼蒼盛也白露疑</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='7901:7950'><span class='krp-note'>戻爲霜然後歳事成國家待禮然後興箋云蒹葭在衆草/之中蒼蒼然彊至白露疑戾爲霜則成而黄㒷者喻衆民</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='7950:7987'><span class='krp-note'>之不從襄公政令者得周/禮以敎之則服薕音廉</span>所謂伊人在水一方<span class='krp-note'>伊/維</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='7987:8034'><span class='krp-note'>也一方難至矣箋云伊當作繄繄猶是也所謂是知周/禮之賢人乃在大水之一邊假喻以言逺繄扵奚反</span>遡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='8034:8072'>洄從之道阻且長<span class='krp-note'>逆流而上曰遡洄逆礼則莫能以/至也箋云此言不以敬順往求之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='8072:8109'><span class='krp-note'>則不能得見遡蘇路/反洄音廻上時掌反</span>遡游從之宛在水中央<span class='krp-note'>順流/而渉</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='8109:8156'><span class='krp-note'>曰遡遊順禮求濟道來迎之箋云宛坐見貌以敬順求/之則近耳易得見也宛紆阮反夲亦作苑易以䜴反</span>蒹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='8156:8184'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0002', 'SBCK', '006-11b' );" name="006-11b" class="pb">[006-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='8184:8222'>葭淒淒白露未晞<span class='krp-note'>淒淒猶蒼蒼也晞乾也箋云云未/晞未為霜淒夲亦作萋七奚反晞</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='8222:8257'><span class='krp-note'>音/希</span>所謂伊人在水之湄<span class='krp-note'>湄水隒也湄音眉/隒魚檢反又音檢</span>遡洄從</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='8257:8293'>之道阻且躋<span class='krp-note'>躋升也箋云升者言其難至/如升阪躋本又作隮子西反</span>遡游從之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='8293:8324'>宛在水中坁<span class='krp-note'>坁小者也/坁直戸反</span>蒹葭采采白露未巳<span class='krp-note'>采/采</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='8324:8359'><span class='krp-note'>猶淒淒也未/巳猶未止也</span>所謂伊人在水之涘<span class='krp-note'>涘厓也/涘音俟</span>遡洄從</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='8359:8391'>之道阻且右<span class='krp-note'>右出其右也箋云右者/言其迂迴也迂音于</span>遡游從之宛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='8391:8407'>在水中沚<span class='krp-note'>小渚曰沚/沚音止</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='8407:8420'>　　　　蒹葭三章章八句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='8420:8439'>終南戒襄公也能取周地始爲諸侯受顯服</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='8439:8458'>大夫美之故作是詩以戒勸之終南何有有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='8458:8486'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0002', 'SBCK', '006-12a' );" name="006-12a" class="pb">[006-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='8486:8514'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0002', 'SBCK', '006-13a' );" name="006-13a" class="pb">[006-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='8514:8533'>黃鳥哀三良也國人刺穆公以人從死而作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='8533:8577'>是詩也<span class='krp-note'>三良三善臣也謂奄息仲行鍼虎也從死自殺/以從死行户郎反下皆同鍼其廉反徐又音針</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='8577:8615'>交交黃鳥止于棘<span class='krp-note'>興也交交小貌黃鳥以時往來得/其所人以壽命終亦得其所箋云</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='8615:8664'><span class='krp-note'>黄鳥止干棘以求安巳也此棘若不安則移興者喻臣之/事君亦然今穆公使臣從死刺其不得黃鳥止于棘之本</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='8664:8699'><span class='krp-note'>意壽音受/又如字</span>誰從穆公子車奄息<span class='krp-note'>子車氏奄息名/箋云言誰從穆</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='8699:8736'><span class='krp-note'>公者/傷之</span>維此奄息百夫之特<span class='krp-note'>乃特百夫之德箋云/百夫之中最雄俊也</span>臨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='8736:8775'>其穴惴惴其慄<span class='krp-note'>惴惴懼也箋云穴謂塚壙中也秦人/哀傷此奄息之死臨視其壙皆爲之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='8775:8812'><span class='krp-note'>悼慄惴之瑞反慄/音栗壙苦晃反</span>彼蒼者天殱我良人<span class='krp-note'>殱盡良善/也箋云言</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='8812:8849'><span class='krp-note'>彼蒼者天愬之殱子廉反/徐又息廉反愬蘇路反</span>如可贖兮人百其身<span class='krp-note'>箋/云</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='8849:8894'><span class='krp-note'>如此奄息之死可以他人贖之者人皆百其身謂/一身百死猶爲之惜善人之甚贖食燭反又音樹</span>交交</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='8894:8922'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0002', 'SBCK', '006-13b' );" name="006-13b" class="pb">[006-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='8922:8947'>黃鳥止于桑誰從穆公子車仲行<span class='krp-note'>箋云仲/行字也</span>維</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='8947:8983'>此仲行百夫之防<span class='krp-note'>防此也箋云防猶當也言比/一人當百夫防徐云毛音方</span>臨其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='8983:9002'>穴惴惴其慄彼蒼者天殱我良人如可贖兮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='9002:9021'>人百其身交交黃鳥止于楚誰從穆公子車</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='9021:9047'>鍼虎維此鍼虎百夫之禦<span class='krp-note'>禦當也禦魚/呂反注同</span>臨其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='9047:9066'>穴惴惴其慄彼蒼者天殱我良人如可贖兮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l272' data-llen='9066:9072'>人百其身</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l273' data-llen='9072:9086'>　　　　黃鳥三章章十二句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l274' data-llen='9086:9105'>晨風刺康公也忘穆公之業始棄其賢臣焉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l275' data-llen='9105:9140'>鴥彼晨風鬱彼北林<span class='krp-note'>興也鴥疾飛貌晨風鸇也欎/積也北林林名也先君招䝨</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l276' data-llen='9140:9168'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0002', 'SBCK', '006-14a' );" name="006-14a" class="pb">[006-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l277' data-llen='9168:9217'><span class='krp-note'>人賢人往之/疾如晨風之飛入比林箋云先君謂穆公/鴥說文作鴧尹橘反字林于叔反鸇字又作/之然反草</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l278' data-llen='9217:9251'><span class='krp-note'>木䟽云似鷂青色說文止仙/反字林巳仙反駃所吏反</span>未見君子憂心欽欽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l279' data-llen='9251:9288'><span class='krp-note'>思望之心中欽欽然箋云言穆公/始未見賢者之時思望而憂之</span>如何如何忘我實</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l280' data-llen='9288:9327'>多<span class='krp-note'>今則忘之矣箋云此以穆公之意責/康公如何如何乎女忘我之事實多</span>山有苞櫟隰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l281' data-llen='9327:9371'>有六駮<span class='krp-note'>檪木也駮如馬倨牙食虎豹箋云山之檪隰之/駮皆其所冝有也以言賢者亦囯家所冝有櫟</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l282' data-llen='9371:9407'><span class='krp-note'>盧狄反駮邦角反獸名草木䟽/云駮馬木名梓榆也倨音據</span>未見君子憂心靡樂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l283' data-llen='9407:9430'>如何如何忘我實多山有苞棣隰有樹檖<span class='krp-note'>棣/唐</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l284' data-llen='9430:9462'><span class='krp-note'>棣也檖赤羅也樂音洛/棣音悌檖音遂或作遂</span>未見君子憂心如醉如</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l285' data-llen='9462:9471'>何如何忘我實多</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l286' data-llen='9471:9485'>　　　　　晨風三章章六句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l287' data-llen='9485:9513'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0002', 'SBCK', '006-14b' );" name="006-14b" class="pb">[006-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l288' data-llen='9513:9532'>無衣刺用兵也秦人刺其君好攻戰亟用兵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l289' data-llen='9532:9566'>而不與民同欲焉<span class='krp-note'>好呼報反下注同攻古弄反/又如字下注同亟欺兾反</span>豈</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l290' data-llen='9566:9603'>曰無衣與子同袍<span class='krp-note'>興也𫀆襺也上與百姓同欲則/百姓樂致其死箋云此責康公</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l291' data-llen='9603:9647'><span class='krp-note'>之言也君豈甞曰女無衣我與女共𫀆乎言/不與民同欲𫀆抱毛反襺古顯反本亦作繭</span>王于興</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l292' data-llen='9647:9681'>師脩我戈矛與子同仇<span class='krp-note'>戈長六尺六寸矛長二丈/天下有道則禮樂征伐自</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l293' data-llen='9681:9730'><span class='krp-note'>天子出仇匹也箋云于於也怨耦曰仇君不與我同欲而/於王興師則云脩我戈矛與子同仇往伐之刺其好攻戰</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l294' data-llen='9730:9768'><span class='krp-note'>仇音求長直亮/反又如字下同</span>豈曰無衣與子同澤<span class='krp-note'>澤潤澤也箋/云澤褻衣近</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l295' data-llen='9768:9810'><span class='krp-note'>汗垢澤如字說文作釋云袴也䙝仙列反近/附近之近汙音烏又汙穢之汙垢古口反</span>王于興師</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l296' data-llen='9810:9838'>修我矛㦸與子偕作<span class='krp-note'>作起也箋云/㦸車㦸常也</span>豈曰無衣與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l297' data-llen='9838:9861'>子同裳王于興師修我甲兵與子偕行<span class='krp-note'>行往/也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l298' data-llen='9861:9889'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0002', 'SBCK', '006-15a' );" name="006-15a" class="pb">[006-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l299' data-llen='9889:9902'>　　　　無衣三章章五句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l300' data-llen='9902:9921'>渭陽康公念母也康公之母晉獻公之女文</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l301' data-llen='9921:9940'>公遭麗姬之難未反而秦姬卒穆公納文公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l302' data-llen='9940:9959'>康公時爲大子贈送文公于渭之陽念母之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l303' data-llen='9959:9978'>不見也我見舅氏如母存焉及其即位而作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l304' data-llen='9978:10015'>是詩也<span class='krp-note'>渭陽音謂水名水北曰陽麗本作/驪同力馳反難乃旦反大音泰</span>我送舅氏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l305' data-llen='10015:10058'>曰至渭陽<span class='krp-note'>母之昆弟曰舅箋云渭水名也秦是時都雍/至渭陽者蓋東行送舅氏於咸陽之地雍於</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l306' data-llen='10058:10097'><span class='krp-note'>用反縣名/今屬扶風</span>何以贈之路車乗黃<span class='krp-note'>贈送也乗黃四馬/也乗繩證反注同</span>我</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l307' data-llen='10097:10123'>送舅氏悠悠我思何以贈之瓊瑰玉佩<span class='krp-note'>瓊瑰石/次玉思</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l308' data-llen='10123:10135'><span class='krp-note'>息嗣反瑰/古囬反</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l309' data-llen='10135:10163'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0002', 'SBCK', '006-15b' );" name="006-15b" class="pb">[006-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l310' data-llen='10163:10176'>　　　　渭陽二章章四句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l311' data-llen='10176:10195'>權輿刺康公也忘先君之舊臣與賢者有始</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l312' data-llen='10195:10227'>而無終也<span class='krp-note'>與音/餘</span>於我乎夏屋渠渠<span class='krp-note'>夏大也箋云/屋具也渠渠</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l313' data-llen='10227:10274'><span class='krp-note'>猶勤勤也言君始於我厚設禮食大具以食我其意勤/勤然夏胡雅反屋如字渠其居反食音嗣注篇内同</span>今</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l314' data-llen='10274:10305'>也毎食無餘<span class='krp-note'>箋云此言君今遇我/薄其食我纔足耳</span>于嗟乎不承權</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l315' data-llen='10305:10340'>輿<span class='krp-note'>承継也權/輿始也</span>於我乎每食四簋<span class='krp-note'>四簋黍稷稲梁/簋音軌内方外</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l316' data-llen='10340:10375'><span class='krp-note'>圎曰簋以盛黍稷外方内圎曰/簠用貯稲粱皆容一斗二升</span>今也毎食不飽于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l317' data-llen='10375:10383'>嗟乎不承權輿</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l318' data-llen='10383:10396'>　　　　權輿二章章五句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l319' data-llen='10396:10411'>秦國十篇二十七章百八十一句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l320' data-llen='10411:10439'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0002', 'SBCK', '006-16a' );" name="006-16a" class="pb">[006-16a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
